### ✅ Test server
GET http://localhost:5000

### ========== AUTH ==========

### Register guru
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama": "Hanif",
  "email": "hanif@gmail.com",
  "password": "hanif123"
}

### Login guru
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "hanif@gmail.com",
  "password": "hanif123"
}

### ========== KELAS ==========

### Tambah kelas
POST http://localhost:5000/api/kelas/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guru_id": 1,
  "nama_kelas": "Kelas 3A",
  "tingkatan": "3"
}

### Ambil semua kelas guru
GET http://localhost:5000/api/kelas/?guru_id=1

### Hapus kelas
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/kelas/1

### ========== SISWA ==========

### Tambah siswa
POST http://localhost:5000/api/siswa/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kelas_id": 1,
  "nama": "Budi Santoso"
}

### Ambil semua siswa
GET http://localhost:5000/api/siswa/?kelas_id=1

### Update level siswa
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/siswa/1/level
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "level_kemampuan": 2
}

### Hapus siswa
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/siswa/1

### ========== SOAL ==========

### Tambah soal
POST http://localhost:5000/api/soal/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cerita": "Pak Budi berangkat ke sawah pagi-pagi bersama anaknya menggunakan sepeda pada pukul 06.30. Mereka melewati sungai dan hutan, hingga tibalah mereka di sawah pada pukul 07.00.",
  "jawaban_jam": 7,
  "jawaban_menit": 0,
  "tingkat_kesulitan": 1
}

### Ambil soal level 1
GET http://localhost:5000/api/soal/?tingkat=1

### Hapus soal
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/soal/1

### ========== SESI ==========

### Submit jawaban benar
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sesi/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "siswa_id": 1,
  "soal_id": 1,
  "jawaban_jam": 7,
  "jawaban_menit": 0,
  "waktu_respons": 8.5,
  "jumlah_koreksi": 1,
  "jumlah_ulang_audio": 0
}

### Submit jawaban salah
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sesi/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "siswa_id": 1,
  "soal_id": 1,
  "jawaban_jam": 6,
  "jawaban_menit": 30,
  "waktu_respons": 15.2,
  "jumlah_koreksi": 3,
  "jumlah_ulang_audio": 2
}

### Riwayat sesi siswa
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sesi/siswa/1

### ========== DASHBOARD ==========

### Ringkasan kelas
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/kelas/1

### Detail performa siswa
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/siswa/1

### Siswa perlu perhatian
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/perhatian/1